        </div>

        <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <!-- Article Header -->
            <header class="mb-10 text-center">
                <div class="mb-6">
                    <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 text-xs font-bold rounded-lg uppercase tracking-wider">
                        <span x-show="lang === 'zh'">
                            产品更新
                            
                        </span>
                        <span x-show="lang === 'en'" x-cloak>
                            Updates
                            
                        </span>
                    </span>
                </div>
                <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight mb-8">
                    <span x-show="lang === 'zh'">以渔账户看板的下一步：把“余额提醒”变成“投放预警”</span>
                    <span x-show="lang === 'en'" x-cloak>Next for Yiyu Dashboards: From Balance Reminders to Media Risk Alerts</span>
                </h1>
                
                <!-- Author Meta -->
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-6 text-sm text-slate-500 border-t border-b border-slate-100 py-4">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <i class="far fa-calendar-alt"></i>
                        <span>2026-05-16</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="h-8 w-px bg-slate-200"></div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <i class="far fa-eye"></i>
                        <span><span id="article-view-count" data-article-id="56" data-base-views="92">92</span> <span x-text="t[lang].reads">阅读</span></span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </header>

            <!-- Featured Image -->
            <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden mb-12 shadow-2xl shadow-slate-200/50">
                <img src="https://picsum.photos/seed/yiyu-20260516-dashboard/800/500" alt="Featured Image" class="w-full h-[400px] object-cover">
            </div>

            <!-- Rich Text Body -->
            <div class="prose max-w-none" x-show="lang === 'zh'">
                <h2>余额低，不等于马上危险</h2>
<p>很多账户管理系统会做余额提醒：低于某个金额就发通知。但在真实投放里，余额 500 美元对一个日耗 80 美元的账户很安全，对一个日耗 900 美元的账户则已经危险。</p>
<p>因此，以渔接下来更关注“投放预警”而不只是“余额提醒”。</p>
<h2>预警要看三个变量</h2>
<p>第一是过去 24 小时日耗。如果账户消耗突然提升，系统需要动态调高提醒优先级。第二是媒体高峰时段，不同国家的量级窗口不同，提醒时间也不能一刀切。第三是充值处理周期，如果某个支付通道在周末速度变慢，系统应提前提示运营。</p>
<p>这三个变量合在一起，才能判断“今天会不会断粮”。</p>
<h2>一个更实际的提醒方式</h2>
<p>与其提醒“账户余额低于 300 美元”，不如提醒：“按当前消耗速度，预计 5 小时后影响投放；建议在欧美晚高峰前完成补款。”后者更像一个投放助手，而不是一个简单闹钟。</p>
<blockquote>
<p>对出海团队来说，看板的目标不是展示更多数字，而是减少关键时刻的误判。</p>
</blockquote>
            </div>
            <div class="prose max-w-none" x-show="lang === 'en'" x-cloak>
                <h2>Low Balance Does Not Always Mean Immediate Risk</h2>
<p>Many account systems send alerts when balance falls below a fixed threshold. But 500 dollars is safe for an account spending 80 dollars per day and risky for one spending 900 dollars per day.</p>
<p>Yiyu’s next dashboard direction is media risk alerts, not only balance reminders.</p>
<h2>Three Variables Matter</h2>
<p>The first is spend in the last 24 hours. If delivery accelerates, the alert priority should rise. The second is market peak time. The third is recharge processing time, especially around weekends or channel delays.</p>
<p>Together, these signals answer a practical question: will this account interrupt delivery today?</p>
<h2>A Better Alert</h2>
<p>Instead of “balance below 300 dollars,” a useful alert says: “At the current spend rate, delivery may be affected in five hours. Complete recharge before the US evening peak.” That is an operations assistant, not a simple alarm.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Social Share (Mock) -->
            <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-between">
